            "title": "lan倫敦首巡穿黑背心大騷肌肉  唱《才二十三》致敬偶像方大同  Hellosss高叫口號為偶像歡呼",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"lan倫敦首巡穿黑背心大騷肌肉  唱《才二十三》致敬偶像方大同  Hellosss高叫口號為偶像歡呼\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/858cd45061b067182c1509361ee31391/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031321155341323.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">lan倫敦首巡穿黑背心大騷肌肉  唱《才二十三》致敬偶像方大同  Hellosss高叫口號為偶像歡呼</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>陳卓賢（lan）昨日（12日）於倫敦 OVO Arena Wembley舉辦首場海外巡迴演唱會《IAN CHAN \"TEARS\" IN MY SIGHT SOLO CONCERT 2025》，成為首位以個人身份衝出香港的MIRROR成員，展開世界巡迴演唱會。 為了支持偶像的首場世界巡迴演唱會，大批Hellosss（Ian粉絲昵稱）早於當日中午已抵達會場，在不同應援地點打卡。下午5時半，粉絲齊集會場對開空地，齊聲高叫口號為偶像歡呼，情緒十分高漲，現場秩序亦非常良好，有當地傳媒採訪支持者有關入場的原因及經過，粉絲紛紛表示：「Ian首站選擇倫敦開演唱會，居於英國嘅香港人一定要支持」、「鍾意Ian可以係冇原因，佢嗰種吸引力我冇辦法解釋，但係就係好想支持佢」、「等Ian嚟倫敦開演唱會已經等咗6年，希望英國有更加多人支持Ian」、「好期待Ian現場唱《鑿》，當然仲希望睇小背心show肌肉！」\n\n</p><h2>親筆信冧爆歌迷</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"lan前日於倫敦 OVO Arena Wembley舉辦首場海外巡迴演唱會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5107e90d69276bf5682c6e4edbea12d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_55_53_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        lan前日於倫敦 OVO Arena Wembley舉辦首場海外巡迴演唱會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian演唱會仍以「Tears」為主題，run down大致上與香港場相同。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/87a19ab99ec4549027be78e3c985a7f9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_55_54_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian演唱會仍以「Tears」為主題，run down大致上與香港場相同。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian演唱時情緒極度投入。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eebf16a97864917e32e9f17ea962cfad/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_55_54_3_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian演唱時情緒極度投入。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"lan自彈自唱，好Charm啊！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e29aefe83157d4195250d097c8bc3205/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_55_55.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        lan自彈自唱，好Charm啊！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"lan唱出《仍在》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7cba0d7110a2f6742c598931fc4e47cb/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_56_04_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        lan唱出《仍在》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"西裝骨骨的lan，好靚仔啊！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/081f5948e4bec91c0afd6f4e2bc0e411/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_56_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西裝骨骨的lan，好靚仔啊！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"lan更唱出《才二十三》，向偶像方大同致敬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f85c3c98fe3c29bdb8aa21a2ef48f0e/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_16_56_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        lan更唱出《才二十三》，向偶像方大同致敬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian認為做幕前要有責任及正能量，就好似方大同一樣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49bb77dadfa098624a51a7d1a701418d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_01_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian認為做幕前要有責任及正能量，就好似方大同一樣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian一身樹熊造型。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb8ba500043337bb1904020a2cfe5e53/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_23_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian一身樹熊造型。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian寵粉度一百分！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02d5a9d1138949689866a1b5c52afc1b/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_23_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian寵粉度一百分！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"除了獻聲，lan更多謝倫敦的歌迷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ca4d4f7af9e0ab7a1d75c4860025886d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        除了獻聲，lan更多謝倫敦的歌迷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>晚上6時，觀眾魚貫入座，居於倫敦的著名填詞人黃偉文（Wyman）亦是座上客。演唱會於晚上7時40分準時開場，Ian一身白色西裝登場，以電結他彈唱《Lost At First Sight》、《DWBF》為演唱會拉開序幕，獻唱《Thank you Postman》時，背幕投射出Ian親筆寫給Hellosss的心聲「To ：All Uk 朋友仔，Thank you for coming！感謝您們與我分享我的第一次巡迴演唱。」寵粉度一百分。演唱會仍以「Tears」為主題，run down大致上與香港場相同，倫敦場就首次現場演唱《鑿》及《玩偶奇遇記》。當演唱《鑿》時，Ian情緒極度投入，粉絲大讚他演繹崩潰情緒時的「變態笑」非常到位；演唱會中段，Ian演唱《才二十三》向偶像方大同致敬，「Dear Mr. Khalil Fong，Thank you for all your inspirations and kindness」，全場觀眾都屏氣凝神欣賞演出。\n\n</p><h2>騷肌唱跳掀高潮</h2>\n<p>至於全晚其中一個高潮位，當然是大家關注的小背心，Ian一身肌肉已做足準備，穿黑色背心跳唱《夜視鏡》及《Sheesh》，令全場粉絲忘我尖叫，Ian完美的二頭肌及胸肌逼爆背心。而倫敦場亦保留了令人感動的一刻，就是《下次愛你》、《另一個諾貝爾》、《仍在》組成的小劇場。至於演唱會尾聲，Ian照舊以樹熊造型作結，大量樹熊紙碎由場館上空傾瀉而下，嘉賓Wyman更在IG出story記錄這美麗畫面，自言被樹熊紙碎活埋。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian穿黑色背心跳唱《夜視鏡》及《Sheesh》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9661f36125de5169f43ef3b26f993393/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_24_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian穿黑色背心跳唱《夜視鏡》及《Sheesh》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian騷肌為全晚其中一個高潮位！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df891ca1f095930d90e4a1243290021b/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_25.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian騷肌為全晚其中一個高潮位！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian向 Hellosss預告下一站是澳洲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7fc96ae4244aa8b15eb9e38bae484944/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_24_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian向 Hellosss預告下一站是澳洲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Ian笑說大家要陪伴樹熊到澳洲巡迴演唱！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ca7443d24c78b64a0a7000f35633e0c9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_13_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Ian笑說大家要陪伴樹熊到澳洲巡迴演唱！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"有來自倫敦的Hellosss（粉絲昵稱）舉起「唯一還有留卓賢多一天」的應援牌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/386d35496f8266e6539df3c6d19faf46/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_17_29_42.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有來自倫敦的Hellosss（粉絲昵稱）舉起「唯一還有留卓賢多一天」的應援牌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>Ian自爆眼濕濕</h2>\n<p>最後Ian向觀眾預告下一站是澳洲，呼籲大家密切期待大會公布詳情，要陪伴樹熊到澳洲巡迴演唱！騷後Ian談及演唱會感受，直言好緊張，因為好在乎今次演出，更透露自己眼濕濕，因在《留一天與你喘息》時，未聽過如此齊整、大聲的大合唱，那刻真心被感動；此外，他亦提到偶像方大同，認為做幕前要有責任、有正能量，就像方大同那樣，對大家起到一個教育的榜樣。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058008/即時-娛樂-lan倫敦首巡穿黑背心大騷肌肉-唱-才二十三-致敬偶像方大同-Hellosss高叫口號為偶像歡呼",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 21:26:25",
