        {
            "title": "上然截收7418票 超額認購逾31倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"上然截收7418票，超額認購逾31倍。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e326654fa83c811a736530066054079b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031320343070803.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">上然截收7418票，超額認購逾31倍。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>萬科香港旗下大埔馬窩路19號新盤上然，將於周六(15日)首輪發售228伙。項目今晚上8時截票，累收7,418票，超額認購逾31倍。\n\n</p>\n<p>萬科香港董事總經理周銘禧表示，上然自開放示範單位以來已錄得逾1.8萬人次參觀，而且市場反應熱烈，期望周六銷售當日買家們能選購心儀單位，銷情理想下不排除會於短期內加推單位應市。\n\n</p>\n<p>抽籤程序將於明天(14日)進行，上然首輪銷售分為A、B兩組發售，A組買家須選購2伙至8伙，而B組買家須選購1伙至8伙。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
